{"tid":1185349,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【比豬隊友激死】隊友太廢「食雞」六小時全輸　16歲少年心臟驟停失救死亡","createTime":"2019-06-04T08:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T12:16:36.000Z","uid":243422,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4363ab309934f13befe7f54a56d9331c32c2e496","tid":1185349,"uid":243422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"《絕地求生》是一款全球知名的大逃殺遊戲，俗稱「食雞」，亦有不少因沉迷這款遊戲而造成的意外。據外媒報道一位印度中史邦的16歲少年（Furkan Quereshi），於5月28日玩PUBG時，連續玩了六小時沒有休息，加上一直被「豬隊友」拖累，一舖雞都食唔到，導致心臟停跳昏迷，家人將其送院急救後無效，最終死亡。<br />\n<br />\n來源：印度時報<br />\n<br />\n「活生生被氣死」的16歲少年Furkan在午餐結束後就開始玩《絕地求生》，家人曾在他玩的過程中要求他休息，但他沒有，而且一玩就是六小時。Furkan的妹妹表示，她看到哥哥的遊戲結束之前，情緒變得非常激動，更對遊戲中的隊友大吼大叫及大罵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1wMY5X8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wMY5X8.png&h=653ad4bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被豬隊友激死的印度青年 Furkan Quereshi<br />\n<br />\nFurkan妹妹稱她哥哥在房間裡突然大喊「爆炸吧！」然後怒掟電話同耳機。仲提到當時她哥哥哭著向隊友怒斥「我以後都唔會再同你玩！因為你搞到我輸咗！」之後就房間內就再無聲音，妹妹就因為好奇而入房查看，只看到Furkan已經癱倒喺床上，於是立即向家人求助。<br />\n<br />\nFurkan被緊急送到醫院搶救，經搶救後依然不治。醫院的心臟科醫師Ashok Jain表示，Furkan送到醫院時已無心跳，他試圖用電擊同注射都無法挽救。雖然Furkan是一位游泳運動員，心臟似乎很健康，「但是遊戲的緊張感會導致腎上腺素激增，令心臟發生驟停。」據報導統計，印度少年沉迷「食雞」的情況非常嚴重，已有高達16名青少年因為玩《絕地求生》而失去性命。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kingofcapture.com/54604/c9%e9%a0%ad%e6%a2%9d/%e8%b1%ac%e9%9a%8a%e5%8f%8b-%e6%bf%80%e6%ad%bb-%e5%b0%91%e5%b9%b4-%e9%a3%9f%e9%9b%9e-%e5%85%a8%e8%bc%b8-%e5%a4%b1%e6%95%91-%e6%ad%bb%e4%ba%a1-ctla1/4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kingofcapture.com%2F54604%2Fc9%25e9%25a0%25ad%25e6%25a2%259d%2F%25e8%25b1%25ac%25e9%259a%258a%25e5%258f%258b-%25e6%25bf%2580%25e6%25ad%25bb-%25e5%25b0%2591%25e5%25b9%25b4-%25e9%25a3%259f%25e9%259b%259e-%25e5%2585%25a8%25e8%25bc%25b8-%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e6%2595%2591-%25e6%25ad%25bb%25e4%25ba%25a1-ctla1%2F4%2F&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgrVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=8e455d5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kingofcapture.com/54604/c9%e9%a0%ad%e6%a2%9d/%e8%b1%ac%e9%9a%8a%e5%8f%8b-%e6%bf%80%e6%ad%bb-%e5%b0%91%e5%b9%b4-%e9%a3%9f%e9%9b%9e-%e5%85%a8%e8%bc%b8-%e5%a4%b1%e6%95%91-%e6%ad%bb%e4%ba%a1-ctla1/4/</a>"},{"pid":"fad89858f29f5f9684707f9773661ecea99d0f8d","tid":1185349,"uid":243422,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10e0bf6aeaa08e1707efbb65c01f05c19817b37","tid":1185349,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:28:44.000Z","msg":"電莖師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5667919f6818a61cc181f625a0cc10725cb7439f","tid":1185349,"uid":122134,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:29:44.000Z","msg":"佩服<br />\n睇得出係尊重隻game<br />\n100%既投入"},{"pid":"42fdc12a999a852db6057ed8acd79f2c13408b4e","tid":1185349,"uid":101253,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"關個隊友撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姓賴？"},{"pid":"8053e07ed5c8ee6c6b0c05ea749658d385b6b047","tid":1185349,"uid":44377,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:39:58.000Z","msg":"點解一篇文可以又書面語又口語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a5f009d4686a628670b5c41f650a9d739beecb","tid":1185349,"uid":19126,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"達哥咁廢都食到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b2fc2fce870b00974090c9f911f4e0c6000fa2","tid":1185349,"uid":131717,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"渣ga<br /